citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:50 a.m. on
August 11th, 2022. I spoke to a Facility Representative, but she was not authorized to do an inspection. She wasn't sure
if the licensee was around. I knocked on the door, but no one answered. I honked the car horn, but no one else
responded. I contacted the licensee by phone and he informed me no one authorized to do the inspection would be
around anytime soon.
End of report.
End Section

narrative:
2.126(b) 
   
Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries. 
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:50 a.m. on 
August 11th, 2022.  I spoke to a Facility Representative, but she was not authorized to do an inspection.  She wasn't sure 
if the licensee was around.  I knocked on the door, but no one answered.  I honked the car horn, but no one else 
responded.  I contacted the licensee by phone and he informed me no one authorized to do the inspection would be 
around anytime soon. 
 
End of report. 
 
 
 
End Section
